    "## Q5 – Covariance\n",
    "\n",
    "Z depends on X directly and also through the term X·Y². Since X and Y are independent standard normals, a lot of cross terms vanish.\n",
    "\n",
    "After expanding carefully, the covariance works out to 2."
   ]
  },
