   "source": [
    "## Q7 – Bit Errors\n",
    "\n",
    "Since the number of bits is large, using a normal approximation saves a lot of work.\n",
    "\n",
    "With the mean and variance plugged in, the probability of more than 120 errors comes out to about 0.015."
   ]
  },
