    "## Q9 – Bivariate Normal\n",
    "\n",
    "From the given mean vector and covariance matrix:\n",
    "\n",
    "- E[X] = E[Y] = 0\n",
    "- Var(X) = Var(Y) = 1\n",
    "- Cov(X, Y) = ρ\n",
    "\n",
    "This one is mostly reading values directly from the matrix."
   ]
  },
